《'''无限飞行II'''》（{{lang-en|''Flight Unlimited II''}}）是[[望远镜工作室|望远镜工作室]]开发、[[史克威尔艾尼克斯欧洲|Eidos交互]]1997年发行的[[飞行模拟器|飞行模拟器]][[电子游戏|电子游戏]]。玩家可从五架飞机任选一架，与多达六百架[[航空交通管制|航空交通管制]]指挥的[[人工智能|人工智能]]飞机在[[舊金山灣區|舊金山灣區]][[领空|领空]]飞行。游戏不像前作《[[无限飞行_(1995年游戏)|无限飞行]]》般注重[[特技飞行|特技飞行]]，改为[[通用航空|通用航空]]玩法，需开发新物理代码和[[游戏引擎|游戏引擎]]，其中物理代码开发主要是因为前作[[计算流体力学|计算流体力学]]系统程序员[[西姆斯·布莱克利|西姆斯·布莱克利]]离职。

开发组希望能带给玩家如[[微軟模擬飛行系列|微軟模擬飛行系列]]般身临其境的感觉。《无限飞行II》的商业表现足以收回成本，评论员称赞游戏图形品质和模拟领空，但整体不及《微软模拟飞行98》。开发组完成本作后分成两队，同时开发《[[无限飞行III|无限飞行III]]》和《飞行战斗》（后更名《[[简氏攻击中队|简氏攻击中队]]》）。两个项目遭遇重重困难，致使公司在2000年倒闭。

== 游戏玩法 ==
[[File:Berryessa_rain.jpg|left]]模式驾驶[[塞斯納172|塞斯納172]]在雨中飞行]]

《无限飞行III》是[[业余飞行模拟器|飞行模拟]]电子游戏，玩家模拟驾驶现实生活中的真实型号飞机<ref name="cgwrev">{{cite magazine | last = Atkin | first = Denny | title = The Sky's Unlimited | magazine = [[電腦遊戲世界|Computer Gaming World]] | date = 1998-04 | issue = 165 | publisher = Ziff Davis | pages = 168, 171}}</ref><ref name="gamespot">{{cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/flight-unlimited-ii-preview/1100-2558717/ | title = ''Flight Unlimited II'' Preview | last = MacDonald | first = T. Liam | date = 1997-06-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201118043833/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/flight-unlimited-ii-preview/1100-2558717/ | archive-date = 2020-11-18 | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-03-30 }}</ref>。玩家可选五种机型，分别是[[塞斯納172|塞斯納172]]、[[派珀切诺基PA28|派珀切诺基PA28]]、[[德哈维兰加拿大DHC-2海狸|德哈维兰加拿大DHC-2海狸]]、[[比奇男爵|比奇男爵58]]、[[P-51戰鬥機|北美航空P51D]]。每架飞机的交互[[驾驶舱|驾驶舱]]均按真实型号设计<ref name="gamespot" /><ref name="flightmanual">{{cite book | last1 = Corbin | first1 = Jim | last2 = F. Tatro | first2 = Ed | last3 = Hantzopoulos | first3 = Constantine | title = Flight Unlimited II ''manual'' | date = 1997-12-12 | publisher = Looking Glass Technologies | pages = 20–25, 27–29, 37, 48, 52, 53, 58, 63, 64, 67, 70, 96, 125, 127}}</ref>，包含模拟[[空速指示器|空速指示器]]、[[航向指示器|航向指示器]]、[[甚高频全向信标|甚高频全向信标]]等[[飛行儀表|飛行儀表]]<ref name="flightmanual" />。玩家可用“快速飞行”模式或[[航空服务基地|航空服务基地]]界面开始飞行，快速飞行模式只需选择机型和飞行条件即可起飞，航空服务基地界面选项更丰富，如教程、[[飛行計劃|飛行計劃]]和历险模式<ref name="flightmanual" />。游戏内置六节教程，指导玩家[[起飛|起飛]]、[[滑行|滑行]]等操作<ref name="pcgamerus">{{cite web | last = Poole | first = Stephen | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20000229144056/http://www.pcgamer.com/reviews/444.html | date = 1998-05 | title = Flight Unlimited II | url = http://www.pcgamer.com/reviews/444.html | work = PC Gamer US | publisher = Future plc | archive-date = 2000-02-29 | access-date = 2000-02-29 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。历险模式属内置任务，目标包括在[[航空母舰|航空母舰]]降落，帮囚犯逃出[[阿爾卡特拉斯島|阿爾卡特拉斯島]]、向[[烛台球场|烛台球场]]空投火鸡等<ref name="pcgamerus" /><ref name="pcgameruk" />，共有25种<ref name="pcgameruk">{{cite web | last = Evans | first = Dean | title = Humbling | url = http://www.pcgamer.co.uk/games/gamefile_review_page.asp?item_id=436 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20020302171300/http://www.pcgamer.co.uk/games/gamefile_review_page.asp?item_id=436 | archive-date = 2002-03-02 | work = PC Gamer UK | publisher = Future plc | dead-url = yes | access-date = 2002-03-02 }}</ref>。

游戏复制[[舊金山灣區|舊金山灣區]]约2.85万平方公里领空为背景<ref name="cgmrev">{{cite web | last = Nolan | first = John | title = ''Flight Unlimited II'' | url = http://www.cdmag.com/articles/009/191/flight_unlimited_2_review.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20050406185445/http://www.cdmag.com/articles/009/191/flight_unlimited_2_review.html | work = Computer Games Magazine | publisher = theGlobe.com | archive-date = 2005-04-06 | date = 1998-01-19 | access-date = 2005-04-06 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，玩家可在46个机场起降<ref name="pcgamerus" />。游戏还模拟雨、风、雾等天气条件<ref name="pcgameruk" />，玩家与多达六百架[[人工智能|人工智能]]飞机共享领空，飞行过程与玩家实时响应<ref name="flightmanual" /><ref name="cgwprev">{{cite magazine | last = Atkin | first = Denny | title = Flight Unlimited II | magazine = Computer Gaming World | publisher = Ziff Davis | date = 1997-07 | issue = 156 | pages = 108, 110}}</ref>。[[航空交通管制|航空交通管制]]实时指示玩家和人工智能飞机防止撞机<ref name="flightmanual" />，玩家可用菜单输入无线电信息与航空交通管制和其他飞机互动<ref name="cgwrev" /><ref name="flightmanual" />。驾驶舱包含三种视角：[[儀器飛行|儀器飛行]]视角支持玩家操纵所有飞行仪表；[[目視飛行規則|目視飛行規則]]主体是大面积[[擋風玻璃|擋風玻璃]]，飞行仪表较少；虚拟驾驶舱视角即自由视角，不能操纵飞行仪表。游戏支持外置摄像头角度，<ref name="flightmanual" />玩家可充当乘客乘坐任何人工智能飞机<ref name="cgwrev" />。

== 开发 ==
1995年的《[[无限飞行_(1995年游戏)|无限飞行]]》完成开发后，项目主管[[西姆斯·布莱克利|西姆斯·布莱克利]]（{{lang|en|Seamus Blackley}}）计划用游戏的[[计算流体力学|计算流体力学]]代码制作[[空战模拟游戏|空战模拟游戏]]《飞行战斗》（''{{lang|en|Flight Combat}}''）<ref name="yee">{{cite magazine | last = yee | first = Bernie | title = Through the Looking Glass | magazine = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer US]] | pages = 62, 63, 65, 67, 69 | volume = 2 | number = 3 | date = 1995-03 | publisher = [[未來出版社|Future plc]]}}</ref><ref name="openingxbox">{{cite book | last = Takahashi | first = Dean | date = 2002-04-23 | title = Opening the Xbox: Inside Microsoft's Plan to Unleash an Entertainment Revolution | publisher = [[普莉瑪遊戲|Prima Lifestyle]] | isbn = 0-7615-3708-2 | url = https://archive.org/details/openingxboxinsid00taka | access-date = 2021-03-30}}</ref><ref name="prnewswire16">{{cite news | date = 1995-06-07 | title = Looking Glass Technologies Ships Flight Unlimited Worldwide | access-date = 2015-11-17 | publisher = [[美通社|PR Newswire]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151117063330/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/LOOKING+GLASS+TECHNOLOGIES+SHIPS+FLIGHT+UNLIMITED+WORLDWIDE-a016983779 | archive-date = 2015-11-17 | dead-url = yes | url = http://www.thefreelibrary.com/LOOKING+GLASS+TECHNOLOGIES+SHIPS+FLIGHT+UNLIMITED+WORLDWIDE-a016983779 }}</ref>。但望远镜工作室新任经理命令他马上为《无限飞行》开发续作，布莱克利拒绝后被炒，1995年末离开公司<ref name="openingxbox" /><ref name="avault1">{{cite web | work = Adrenaline Vault | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/19990501201130/http://www.avault.com/articles/seamus.asp | access-date = 1999-05-01 | last = Laprad | first = David | title = The Evolution of the Prehistoric Beast: An Interview with ''Trespasser'' Project Leader Seamus Blackley | url = http://www.avault.com/articles/seamus.asp | date = 1998-09-08 | archive-date = 1999-05-01 }}</ref>，康斯坦丁·汉佐普洛斯（{{lang|en|Constantine Hantzopoulos}}）当上首席设计师和《无限飞行II》14人开发团队的项目主管<ref name="gamespot" /><ref name="boston2">{{cite news | last = Von Hoffman | first = Constantine | title = Software Company Plays Games Against the Competition | date = 1997-07-22 | newspaper = Boston Herald | publisher = Herald Media Inc. | at = Business; p. 24}}</ref>。开发组不像前作那样注重[[特技飞行|特技飞行]]，改用[[通用航空|通用航空]]玩法<ref name="gamespot" />，旨在与[[微軟模擬飛行系列|微軟模擬飛行系列]]竞争<ref name="boston">{{cite news | last = Saunders | first = Michael | date = 1997-12-15 | title = Flights of Fancy for Virtual Pilots | newspaper = [[波士頓環球報|The Boston Globe]] | publisher = The New York Times Company | at = Living; p. C.8 }}</ref>。望远镜工作室1996年12月18日公布新作开发计划，声称共有六架飞机，45个机场和旧金山湾区约2.2万平方公里地形<ref name="pressrelease">{{cite press release | last = Betourney | first = Susan | title = Looking Glass Studios Redefines Flight Simulators Again | date = 1996-12-18 | publisher = Looking Glass Studios | location = Cambridge, Massachusetts | url = http://www.lglass.com/c_info/f2_pr.html | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/19980526172821/http://www.lglass.com/c_info/f2_pr.html | archive-date = 1998-05-26 | access-date = 1998-05-26 }}</ref>。选中旧金山湾区主要是因为这里景观多变、机场众多<ref name="avault">{{cite web | last = Pagliarulo | first = Emil | url = http://www.avault.com/previews/flight.asp | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/19971014041530/http://www.avault.com/previews/flight.asp | title = Flight Unlimited 2 | work = Adrenaline Vault | archive-date = 1997-10-14 | access-date = 1997-10-14 }}</ref>。1997年1月，[[史克威尔艾尼克斯欧洲|Eidos交互]]与望远镜工作室合作负责游戏营销和发行<ref name="pressrelease2">{{cite press release | title = Looking Glass Studios Announces Exclusive Four-Year Publishing and Distribution Agreement with Eidos Interactive | location = Cambridge, Massachusetts | url = http://www.lglass.com/c_info/eidos_pr.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/19980526172800/http://www.lglass.com/c_info/eidos_pr.html | archive-date = 1998-05-26 | date = 1997-01-27 | publisher = Looking Glass Studios | access-date = 1998-05-26 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。
[[File:CGfog.jpg|thumb]]算法提升[[帧率|帧率]]，开发组为《无限飞行II》开发ZOAR渲染器，无需采用距离模糊算法<ref name="cgwprev" /><ref name="avault" />]]

开发组决定不沿用前作技术。布莱克利告诉汉佐普洛斯，游戏应该重新营造真实飞行的“内在感受”，但布莱克利的计算流体力学系统代码“全是黑匣子[[面条式代码|面条式代码]]”，开发组根本看不懂。<ref name="gamespot" />曾参与制作《[[Falcon_4.0|Falcon 4.0]]》等飞行模拟器的程序员吉姆·贝里（{{lang|en|Jim Berry}}）根据[[向量|力学矢量]]计算编写新物理代码取代计算流体力学系统<ref name="gamespot" /><ref name="cgmrev" />。汉佐普洛斯、贝里与设计师埃德·塔特罗（{{lang|en|Ed Tatro}}）、特技飞行员[[迈克尔·古利安|迈克尔·古利安]]（{{lang|en|Michael Goulian}}）乘飞机为新物理代码收集数据，詹姆斯·弗莱明（{{lang|en|James Fleming}}）编写游戏新地形渲染器ZOAR<ref name="gamespot" />。《无限飞行》采用[[距离模糊|距离模糊]]限制可见地形，这会导致[[绘制距离|显示距离]]突然变化，开发组设法在续作避免<ref name="cgwprev" /><ref name="avault" />。新[[游戏引擎|游戏引擎]]不再删除[[材质贴图|纹理]]，采用[[Mipmap|Mipmapping]]减少远处地形的多边形数量<ref name="gamespot" />，增加可视区域同时又能用雾充当大气效果，不再用作遮挡画面的手段<ref name="cgwprev" />。

开发组立志创造“最好、最真实的民用飞行模拟器”<ref name="avault" />，为玩家提供身临其境的虚拟世界<ref name="cgmprev">{{cite web | publisher = theGlobe.com | archive-date = 2005-04-06 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20050406185449/http://www.cdmag.com/articles/002/108/flight_unlimited_2_preview.html | url = http://www.cdmag.com/articles/002/108/flight_unlimited_2_preview.html | title = Flight Unlimited II | last = Smith | first = Peter | year = 1997 | work = Computer Games Magazine | access-date = 2005-04-06}}</ref>。航空交通管制、人工智能飞机和玩家间的无线电通信实时发生，用“复杂的音频拼接系统”把预录语音片段融合成符合实际情况的语句<ref name="gamespot" /><ref name="cgmprev" />。开发组录下各型号真实飞机发动机的声音，驾驶舱与前作相比交互功能更丰富，地形区域约为前作三百倍<ref name="gamespot" />。他们把[[数字地面模型|数字地面模型]]和[[卫星影像|卫星影像]]结合，每像素代表四平方米来生成地形<ref name="cgwprev" />。影像是在上午九点半拍摄，这时的阴影够长，足以形成视觉深度<ref name="gamespot" />。超过九层的建筑用[[三维模型|三维模型]]渲染<ref name="cgwprev" />。精细的地形令玩家得以体验目视飞行规则<ref name="gamespot" />。开发组原计划只提供目视飞行模式，后来增加仪器飞行令导航更轻松<ref name="combatsim">{{cite web | title = E3: The Third Report | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160817090646/http://www.combatsim.com/archive/htm/htm_arc1/e3_3.htm | access-date = 2021-03-31 | url = http://www.combatsim.com/archive/htm/htm_arc1/e3_3.htm | work = Combatsim | date = 1997-06-23 | archive-date = 2016-08-17 }}</ref>，游戏发行后还计划增加地形和多玩家模式<ref name="cgmprev" />。

1997年6月，《无限飞行II》与《[[神偷：暗黑计划|神偷：暗黑计划]]》一起在[[E3电子娱乐展|E3电子娱乐展]]展出<ref name="diary">{{cite web | last = Stellmach | first = Tim | date = 1997-06-27 | publisher = Looking Glass Studios | archive-date = 1998-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/19980224014225/http://www.lglass.com/p_info/dark/darkdiary.html | dead-url = yes | url = http://www.lglass.com/p_info/dark/darkdiary.html#6-27-97 | title = Thief: The Dark Project Project Diary | access-date = 1998-02-24}}</ref>，望远镜工作室详细介绍包括任务在内的早期计划<ref name="combatsim" />。《无限飞行II》普受好评<ref name="boston2" /><ref name="diary" />，战斗模拟网（COMBATSIM.COM）称赞本作达到“民航模拟飞行新境界”<ref name="combatsim" />。《[[電腦遊戲世界|電腦遊戲世界]]》的丹尼·阿特金（{{lang|en|Denny Atkin}}）很喜欢本作，但觉得望远镜工作室选择在民用航空而非战斗飞行模拟器市场厮杀有些不智<ref name="boston2" />。同年八月，望远镜工作室与想打入电子游戏行业的技术公司[[AverStar|Intermetrics]]合并<ref name="pr5">{{cite news | title = Eidos Interactive to Publish Games From Looking Glass | date = 1997-09-09 | work = [[美國商業資訊|Business Wire]] | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170107101316/http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Eidos+Interactive+to+Publish+Games+From+Looking+Glass%3B+Flight...-a019731567 | access-date = 2017-01-07 | archive-date = 2017-01-07 | url = http://www.thefreelibrary.com/Eidos+Interactive+to+Publish+Games+From+Looking+Glass%3B+Flight...-a019731567}}</ref><ref name="diary2">{{cite web | last = Stellmach | first = Tim | date = 1997-08-15 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/19980224043504/http://www.lglass.com/p_info/dark/darkdiary.html | access-date = 1998-02-24 | url = http://www.lglass.com/p_info/dark/darkdiary.html#8-15-97 | title = Thief: The Dark Project Project Diary | publisher = Looking Glass Studios | archive-date = 1998-02-24}}</ref><ref name="neurath">{{cite web | last = Weise | first = Matthew | date = 2012-03-04 | title = Looking Glass Studios Interview Series – Audio Podcast 10 – Paul Neurath | url = http://gambit.mit.edu/updates/2012/03/looking_glass_studios_intervie_7.php | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210205033605/http://gambit.mit.edu/updates/2012/03/looking_glass_studios_intervie_7.php | publisher = Singapore-MIT GAMBIT Game Lab | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-02-05 | access-date = 2021-03-31}}</ref>。此次合并主要是为解决财务困境<ref name="neurath" />，望远镜工作室在1997年中期大裁员<ref name="leonard">{{Cite journal | archive-date = 2021-03-03 | title = Postmortem: Thief: The Dark Project | url = https://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/131762/postmortem_thief_the_dark_project.php | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210303044924/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/feature/131762/postmortem_thief_the_dark_project.php | last = Leonard | first = Tom | journal = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 1999-07-09 | access-date = 2021-03-31}}</ref>，公司的蒂姆·斯泰尔马赫（{{lang|en|Tim Stellmach}}）与保罗·诺拉特（{{lang|en|Paul Neurath}}）宣称这是友好合并，斯泰尔马赫还称“交易期间大家都对《无限飞行II》与《神偷：暗黑计划》感到非常激动”<ref name="diary2" /><ref name="neurath" />。Eidos交互九月接手《无限飞行II》发行<ref name="pr5" />，游戏1997年12月12日面世<ref name="ign6">{{cite web | title = Flight Unlimited II | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080115185450/http://pc.ign.com/objects/003/003103.html | access-date = 2008-01-15 | url = http://pc.ign.com/objects/003/003103.html | website = [[IGN|IGN]] | archive-date = 2008-01-15 | dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

